<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="play-v">play <strong><em>v</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /pleɪ/    美 /pleɪ/  </p>
<p>vt &amp; vi</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>做 (游戏)；玩耍；娱乐：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Show us how to play the game, will you? 
你能教我们怎么玩这个游戏吗？</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The streets I used to play in are jammed with cars now.
我过去经常玩耍的街道如今堵满了汽车。</p><footer>2010 浙江</footer></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Kathy picked up a lot of Spanish by <strong>playing with</strong> the native boys and girls.
通过跟当地孩子一起玩，凯西学会了很多西班牙语。</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>参加 (体育活动、比赛等)：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>play basketball / volleyball
打篮球/排球</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>play cards / bridge
打纸牌 / 桥牌</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The Houston Rockets will <strong>play against</strong> the Los Angeles Lakers. 
休斯敦火箭队将对阵洛杉矶湖人队。</p></div>

<h4 id="3">3.★ <strong>弹奏；演奏；扮演；演出：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>play the guitar 
弹吉他</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>They’re playing the National Anthem. 
他们在奏国歌。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Last year he <strong>played a</strong> major <strong>part in</strong> the school play.
去年，他在校园剧中扮演了一个重要角色。</p><footer>人教⑦ – 1</footer></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>This scene doesn’t play so well. 
这一场演得并不好。</p></div>

<h4 id="4">4.★ <strong>播放 (唱片、磁带等)：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Play their new CD for me, please. 
请把他们的新唱片放给我听一下吧。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="play-with">play with</h3>
<p>1.<strong>玩弄：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Stop playing with your food!
别老是摆弄食物！</p></div></div>